      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is quite different from makeArrayDefault in that it does export the UB (there are no Ts in the returned memory, since it also doesn\u0027t even default initialize so non-trivial types don\u0027t have constructors run). It\u0027s somewhat strange to claim this returns a T*, what does this really provide over makeBytesAlignedTo?",
